library(mgcv)
library(visreg)
df1 <- read.csv("output/final_functions.csv")
# fit a smooth which varies by comparison_type
df1$type <- factor(df1$type)
b <- gam(dist_search ~ s(stage, k = 4, fx = TRUE, by = type) + type, data = df1, family = quasibinomial(link="logit"), method = "REML")

library(mgcv)

df <- read.csv("output/final_visual.csv")
df2 <- subset(df, df$type != "simple")

library(modelsummary)
options("modelsummary_format_numeric_latex" = "plain")
models <- list(
"Functions vs Visual Search" =  gam(dist_search ~ s(stage, k = 4, fx = TRUE, by = type) + type, data = df1, family = betar(link="logit"), method = "REML"),
"Visual Search" = gam(dist_search ~ s(stage, k = 4, fx = TRUE, by = type) + type, data = df2, family = betar(link="logit"), method = "REML")
)

             estimate = "estimate",
             stars = TRUE,              
             statistic = c("Std.Error" = "std.error", 
                           "t-value" = "statistic"))
